            <summary>Deed of sale of land by Gaspero and Antonio del Pero of Pistoia to the Vallombrosan Don Niccolò di Giovanni, abbot of the Tau church of Pistoia (referred to as San Salvatore a Fonte Taona in the manuscript). Notarized by Niccolò di Bartolomeo del Gallo on 15 July 1474. Filed with the document is a short, later summary written in Italian on paper.</summary>
